It's a flower that I randomly placed. Somehow, I feel like
it's growing.

In the closet, there are several identical white dresses.
With this, even Curry Udon won't be scary anymore.

It's Lunaroa's dressing table... for some reason, it looks
even more beautiful than my own.

Lunaroa and I bought these matching flowers together... I
feel like I might be the one to make them wither first.

We bought flowers together and they seem to be growing more
vigorously than mine...

I impulsively bought a scale at the store. Well... it's
cool, you know...!... But it's quite annoying swaying
around.

her...

I'm worried...

\SE[17] (Tita has become quite dependent on taking care of

let's equip it right away.
\SE[13]I feel like it might not be useful anymore...

\SE[2]Welcome back, Laura. \SE[13]Please fight in my

\SE[12] Even when Lunaroa-sama is sleeping, she is

\SE[21]I know it's not much, but I hope it's enough to put

\SE[15]Leave it to me. \SE[15]Don't worry. Leave it to me,
big sister.

\SE[7]I can only support you... \!\SE[13]But still, do your
best... Laura.
